okay so if you watch this show you probably know, we are believers in the free to play model

00:00:16.980 --> 00:00:20.460
We think it has the potential to be one of the best things to happen to video games

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:22.760
allowing consumers to pay what they feel a game is worth.

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:28.460
while at the same time making sure that game developers don't miss out on customers who might not be able to afford the full retail price

00:00:28.460 --> 00:00:33.180
or customers who are willing pay far far more then standard retail value for a expanded experience

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:36.380
in an ideal scenario this model is fantastic!

